tay ALIVE!</strong>.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1497590/extras/45ebbf1b35e20247510bf4dd9260fcaa.avif?t=1659367918\" width=600 height=227 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Kill all Saints before they detect you.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Give Saints a silent and hidden dead using Silent Step and Vision abilities.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>With blackout and lockdown abilities ambush Saints.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Mingle with Saints by pretending you are completing the tasks.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Blame others in voting sessions to get rid of executions.</li></ul>",
